00:31:18.510 --> 00:31:21.080
So another key tool
is using cliffhangers.

00:31:21.080 --> 00:31:23.160
And so creating the
cliffhangers, whether it's

00:31:23.160 --> 00:31:25.971
in advertising, or
in your storytelling,

00:31:25.971 --> 00:31:28.220
or maybe just a cliffhanger
to get people to come back

00:31:28.220 --> 00:31:29.150
to the next meeting.

00:31:29.150 --> 00:31:32.770
Captures attention again
because of that uncertainty gap.

00:31:32.770 --> 00:31:36.770
You should use cliffhangers
when you can unless you're

00:31:36.770 --> 00:31:38.370
going through a press crisis.

