Couple different examples.

00:42:34.970 --> 00:42:37.159
Green is terrible
packaging in China

00:42:37.159 --> 00:42:39.700
because green is associated with
funerals and death in China.

00:42:39.700 --> 00:42:42.680
And in fact, it is a very poor
performing packaging color

00:42:42.680 --> 00:42:44.190
in that country.

00:42:44.190 --> 00:42:47.200
Red has significantly
different associations

00:42:47.200 --> 00:42:48.460
across different cultures.

00:42:48.460 --> 00:42:50.550
There are a few things
that are the same.

00:42:50.550 --> 00:42:52.234
Like for example, blue.

00:42:52.234 --> 00:42:54.650
If you, for example, there was
a study that actually found

00:42:54.650 --> 00:42:57.410
that if you put schizophrenics
under blue light, regardless

00:42:57.410 --> 00:42:59.750
of which culture,
they will be calmer

00:42:59.750 --> 00:43:01.722
and they will be more relaxed.

00:43:01.722 --> 00:43:03.180
And if you put them
in a red light,

00:43:03.180 --> 00:43:05.000
they will be more energetic
and they'll be more jumpy

00:43:05.000 --> 00:43:06.380
and they'll be more agitated.

00:43:06.380 --> 00:43:08.050
So there are some
that are universal.

00:43:08.050 --> 00:43:10.383
But there's a lot that are
different culture by culture.

00:43:10.383 --> 00:43:12.670
And I actually provide
some resources in the book

00:43:12.670 --> 00:43:14.944
and some links and examples
of different colors

00:43:14.944 --> 00:43:15.860
in different cultures.

00:43:15.860 --> 00:43:17.190
And there's actually
an amazing color wheel

00:43:17.190 --> 00:43:19.560
that shows the associations
different cultures have

00:43:19.560 --> 00:43:20.580
with different cultures.

00:43:20.580 --> 00:43:22.205
The reason why I
focus so much on color

00:43:22.205 --> 00:43:26.200
is because color provides the
majority of initial assessment

00:43:26.200 --> 00:43:27.890
when people are
looking at a brand.

00:43:27.890 --> 00:43:30.710
If people look at a
symbol for the first time,

00:43:30.710 --> 00:43:33.350
the majority of their assessment
will be purely from the color

00:43:33.350 --> 00:43:34.800
as well.

